OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Frain will soon clear away north, then
OL,7,Fdry with a few clear spells in the
OL,8,Fevening. Cloud and patchy light rain
OL,9,Fwill then spread east overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA cloudy start with the odd
OL,12,Fspot of light rain. Bright spells
OL,13,Fdeveloping through the morning then
OL,14,Ffurther rain is likely for a time in
OL,15,Fthe late afternoon and evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,18,Fwarm with variable cloud and bright
OL,19,Fspells through the weekend and on
OL,20,FMonday. Mainly dry on Saturday and
OL,21,FMonday, but rain for a time on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
